title: Fruit Cocktail Coconut Cake
ingredients: ['For the cake', '250g plain flour', '300g caster sugar', '1 1/2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 eggs', '1 (420g) tin fruit cocktail', 'For the topping', '110g dark brown soft sugar', '115g walnuts, chopped', '75g desiccated coconut', 'For the icing', '110g margarine', '235ml golden syrup', '2 (170g) tins evaporated milk', '75g desiccated coconut']
